br />\n<br />\n我冇記錯美國係行OMO同Core inflation<br />\n<br />\nOMO係透過買賣自己國債公債地方借去控制market cash availability<br />\n從而達到影響息口<br />\n<br />\n美國買債會 增加市場美金cash, interest rate drop<br />\n狂放錢出黎係當年qe做法, 刺激經濟<br />\n<br />\nPS. Monetary policy係較macro, fiscal policy 係micro tuning<br />\n<br />\nOther way round, 經濟過熱想收一收<br />\n<br />\n美國賣債美金回籠,息口抽上去<br />\n<br />\nAlthough not strong, 都係依家個trending<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港linked exchange rate system<br />\n<br />\n主要透過三間引錢錢行同central 操作"},{"pid":"5b0f83ad4cb3b859045da1315f5ab52fb6b82c62","tid":1513914,"uid":52192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d858a39ba9215ffe3b84e0a1f8e75ff1cc1bcb5d","tid":1513914,"uid":52192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c778c9eecab94d9ac55f7bf9c6137a67cbb66a3f","tid":1513914,"uid":52192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"呢個係monetary policy問題<br />\n<br />\n方間4大類(唔代表全部)<br />\n<br />\n1.OMO<br />\n<br />\n2.Reserve rate<br />\n<br />\n3.Targeted inflation Core or non core<br />\n<br />\n4.Linked exchange rate"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:17:39.000Z","msg":"首先想問樓主所謂穩住HKD率價係咩意思<br />\n<br />\n第二,我地要理解香港係link邊度既currency<br />\n<br />\n係美國<br />\n<br />\n我冇記錯美國係行OMO同Core inflation<br />\n<br />\nOMO係透過買賣自己國債公債地方借去控制market cash availability<br />\n從而達到影響息口<br />\n<br />\n美國買債會 增加市場美金cash, interest rate drop<br />\n狂放錢出黎係當年qe做法, 刺激經濟<br />\n<br />\nPS. Monetary policy係較macro, fiscal policy 係micro tuning<br />\n<br />\nOther way round, 經濟過熱想收一收<br />\n<br />\n美國賣債美金回籠,息口抽上去<br />\n<br />\nAlthough not strong, 都係依家個trending<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港linked exchange rate system<br />\n<br />\n主要透過三間引錢錢行同central 操作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"Central 係香港我指MA and 外匯儲備金(usd)<br />\n<br />\nIn linked exchange rate system, 你要有over 100% 既外匯去support你local currency hkd<br />\n<br />\n三間bank可以套利地向central換錢,呢個係auto adjustment機制<br />\n<br />\n當美金對hkd貴左, say from 7.8 to 8 , 3 banks 就自然會用7.8港元去買usd1賺20cents差價<br />\n<br />\n同時hkd流通量少左利率就會向上<br />\n<br />\n錯覺係hk 利率向上就可以穩住港元對美金"}]}